Correct Order (DevOps Lifecycle)

Terraform → Infra provisioning (AWS VPC, EC2, EKS cluster)

Jenkins → CI/CD orchestrator

SonarQube → Code Quality & Coverage analysis

OWASP Dependency Check → Dependency vulnerability scan

Trivy → Container & Image vulnerability scan

Docker → Build & package application into container

Nexus → Artifact & Docker image repository

Kubernetes (EKS) → Deploy & orchestrate containers

Helm → Package and manage k8s deployments

ArgoCD → GitOps for automated deployment

Prometheus → Metrics collection & monitoring

Grafana → Visualization dashboards

Loki → Centralized logging for containers

ELK Stack (Elastic, Logstash, Kibana) → Advanced logging/analytics (optional alongside Loki)
